These scripts reqire iptables-persistent. Execute following command to install.

1. Install 'iptables-persistent'.

apt install iptables-persistent


2. Put 'dl_iplist' on /etc/cron.monthly.

mv dl_iplist /etc/cron.monthly/


3. Execute following

bash syssecurity.sh       # Run once only
bash makerules.sh
bash iptables.sh

Now you got iron wall!
